---
title: Terroir.ma — Modular Monolith Architecture
---
graph TD
    subgraph NestJS["NestJS Application (Port 3000)"]
        CM[CooperativeModule\nschema: cooperative]
        PM[ProductModule\nschema: product]
        CertM[CertificationModule\nschema: certification]
        NM[NotificationModule\nschema: notification]
    end

    subgraph DB["PostgreSQL 16 + PostGIS 3.4 (Port 5432)"]
        S1[(cooperative schema)]
        S2[(product schema)]
        S3[(certification schema)]
        S4[(notification schema)]
    end

    subgraph Infra["Infrastructure"]
        K[Redpanda\nKafka-compatible\nPort 9092]
        R[Redis\nQR cache\nPort 6379]
        KC[Keycloak 24\nJWT auth\nPort 8443]
        MP[Mailpit\nDev SMTP\nPort 8025]
    end

    CM --> S1
    PM --> S2
    CertM --> S3
    NM --> S4

    CM <-->|events| K
    PM <-->|events| K
    CertM <-->|events| K
    NM <-->|events| K

    CertM --> R
    NestJS -->|JWT validation| KC
    NM -->|SMTP| MP

    style CM fill:#e3f2fd
    style PM fill:#e8f5e9
    style CertM fill:#fff3e0
    style NM fill:#fce4ec
    style NestJS fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#bdbdbd
